Package primes

Class Summary
PrimeNumberSeeker This class is a Thread that continuously finds new prime numbers
and sleeps for a specified delay time afterwards.
Primes This is a servlet with the only intention to redirect all requets
to the searcher servlet.
Searcher This is a Web Servlet, handling a prime number seeker and displaying
the current prime number that was discovered last whenever the
Servlet gets refreshed.
